<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id9088f730-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s5301"><num value="5301">§ 5301.</num><heading> Short title</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter may be cited as the “Exchange Rates and International Economic Policy Coordination Act of 1988”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id9088f731-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/418/tIII/s3001">Pub. L. 100–418, title III, § 3001</ref>, <date date="1988-08-23">Aug. 23, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/1372">102 Stat. 1372</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id9088f732-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id9088f733-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id9088f734-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This subchapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this subtitle”, meaning subtitle A (§§ 3001–3006) of title III of <ref href="/us/pl/100/418">Pub. L. 100–418</ref>, <date date="1988-08-23">Aug. 23, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/1372">102 Stat. 1372</ref>, which is classified principally to this subchapter. For complete classification of subtitle A to the Code, see Tables.</p>
</note>
</notes>
